# 28. Mahjong Table Remaking (麻将桌重制)

**Description:**

来检查大家总结赛有没有好好补题了。

还记得总结赛的麻将桌绘制吗，没错一年一度的川麻大赛马上就要举办了，同样也需要绘制麻将桌，但显然川麻更高级，所以麻将桌绘制的规则也复杂一些。

现在给你这个牌桌的长和宽，以及圆形和正方形的信息，请你帮忙绘制出整张牌桌。如果不需要贴麻将 ![l o g o](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2219%22%20width%3D%2233%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%3E%3Cmi%3El%3C%2Fmi%3E%3Cmi%3Eo%3C%2Fmi%3E%3Cmi%3Eg%3C%2Fmi%3E%3Cmi%3Eo%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Arial%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%222.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3El%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Arial%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%228.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Eo%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Arial%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2217.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Eg%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Arial%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2226.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Eo%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E) 的，请输出 '\'，否则请输出 '/'（不含引号）。你的输出应该保证牌桌的左上角在你输出的第一个字符。

，表示矩形的两个对角端点，保证生成的正方形四个顶点都在格点上。

**Output:**

输出共 ![w](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2219%22%20width%3D%2214%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%3E%3Cmi%3Ew%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Arial%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%226.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Ew%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E) 行，每行 ![h](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2219%22%20width%3D%2211%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%3E%3Cmi%3Eh%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Arial%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%224.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Eh%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E) 个字符，为 '\' 或 '/'（不含引号）。

**Example:**

- Input:

```
11 11
5 5 3
6 2 4 8
```

- Output:

```
\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\//\\\\\
\\\/////\\\

\\//////\\\

\\\\\\\\\\\
```
